MOST IMMEDIATE
No.1/34/1/2012-Cab.
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 27th October, 2012
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 27th October, 2012:
(i)
Shri S.M. Krishna relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of External Affairs;
Smt. Ambika Soni relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Information and
Broadcasting;
(iii) Shri Subodh Kant Sahay relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Tourism;
(ii)
(iv) Shri Mukul Wasnik relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of Social Justice
and Empowerment;
(v)
Shri Mahadev S. Khandela relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State
in the Ministry of Tribal Affairs;
(vi) Shri Vincent Pala relinquished the charge of (a) the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Water Resources; and (b) the office of the Minister of State in the Ministry of
Minority Affairs; and
(vii) Ms. Agatha Sangma relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of State in the
Ministry of Rural
lopment.
(K.L. Sharma)
for Cabinet Secretary
